## Database Categorization

### MAIN ADMIN DATABASE (Central Warehouse + Platform Management)

| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `main_admin` | Main admin user accounts |
| `sub_main_admin` | Sub-admin accounts under main admin |
| `buying_group_domains` | Domain mappings for tenant resolution |
| **BUYING GROUP ADMIN ACCOUNTS** | |
| `admin` | Buying group admin accounts (created by MainAdmin; used for BG portal login against Main Admin DB) |
| **WAREHOUSE OPERATIONS** | |
| `warehouses` | Warehouse locations |
| `return_transactions` | Main return transaction records |
| `return_transaction_items` | Line items within returns |
| `return_batches` | Batched returns for processing |
| `batch_workflow_steps` | Workflow state for batches |
| `warehouse_discrepancies` | Discrepancy tracking |
| `debit_memos` | Debit memos for returns |
| `debit_memo_items` | Line items in debit memos |
| `ra_requests` | Return Authorization requests |
| `shipment_groups` | Shipment groupings |
| `wine_cellar_items` | Items in wine cellar (aging) |
| `destruction_records` | Destruction tracking |
| **REFERENCE DATA** | |
| `reverse_distributors` | Reverse distributor partners |
| `manufacturer_policies` | Manufacturer return policies |
| `manufacturer_return_policies` | Detailed return policy rules |
| `manufacturer_policy_notes` | Policy notes |
| `non_returnable_products` | Products excluded from returns |
| `ndc_pricing` | NDC pricing book |
| `distributors` | Distributor records |

