## MainAdmin Portal Deep Analysis

### Pages (34 total)

| Route | APIs Called | Key Tables | Key RPCs |
|-------|-------------|------------|----------|
| `/` (Dashboard) | `GET /main-admin/buying-groups`, `GET /admin/warehouse/received`, `GET /admin/batches` | - | `get_buying_groups_list`, `warehouse_list_received`, `list_batches` |
| `/login` | `POST /main-admin/auth/login` | `main_admin`, `sub_main_admin` | `get_main_admin_by_email`, `get_sub_main_admin_by_email` |
| `/setup-account` | `GET /main-admin/sub-admins/invite/validate`, `POST .../accept` | `sub_main_admin` | `validate_sub_admin_invite_token`, `accept_sub_admin_invite` |
| `/buying-groups` | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /main-admin/buying-groups`, `GET .../domains` | `admin` (Main Admin DB), `admin_settings` (BG DB), `buying_group_domains` (Main Admin DB) | `get_buying_groups_list`, `create_buying_group`, `update_buying_group` |
| `/sub-admins` | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /main-admin/sub-admins` | `sub_main_admin` | `get_sub_main_admins_list`, `create_sub_main_admin`, `update_sub_main_admin` |
| `/settings` | `GET/PATCH /admin/settings`, `POST .../upload-logo`, `POST .../reset-password` | `admin_settings`, `warehouses` | `get_admin_settings`, `update_admin_settings`, `get_default_warehouse` |
| `/distributors` | `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /admin/distributors` | `distributors` | `get_admin_distributors_list`, `create_admin_distributor` |
| `/policies` | `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /admin/policies` | `manufacturer_policies`, `manufacturer_return_policies` | Direct table access |
| `/ndc-pricing` | `GET /admin/ndc-pricing/search`, `POST/DELETE /admin/ndc-pricing` | `ndc_pricing` | `search_ndc_pricing_book`, `upsert_ndc_pricing` |
| `/pharmacy-payments` | `GET /admin/pharmacy-payments`, `POST .../calculate` | `pharmacy_payments` | `pharmacy_payment_list`, `pharmacy_payment_calculate` |
| `/warehouse/receiving` | `GET /admin/warehouse/pending`, `POST /admin/warehouse/scan-box` | `return_transactions` | `warehouse_list_pending`, `warehouse_scan_box` |
| `/warehouse/verification` | `GET /admin/warehouse/received` | `return_transactions` | `warehouse_list_received` |
| `/warehouse/verification/[id]` | `POST .../start-verification`, `PATCH .../verify-v2` | `return_transactions`, `warehouse_discrepancies` | `warehouse_start_verification`, `warehouse_verify_item_v2` |
| `/warehouse/batches` | `GET /admin/batches`, `POST /admin/batches` | `return_batches` | `list_batches`, `create_batch` |
| `/warehouse/returns` | `GET /return-transactions`, `POST .../pause`, `POST .../complete` | `return_transactions` | `list_return_transactions`, `change_return_transaction_status` |
| `/warehouse/debit-memos` | `GET /admin/debit-memos/grouped-by-return` | `debit_memos` | `list_debit_memos_grouped_by_return` |
| `/warehouse/ra-tracking` | `GET /admin/ra-tracking`, `POST .../request-ra` | `ra_requests` | `ra_list_tracking`, `ra_send_request` |

