## Cross-Database Access Analysis

### Admin Portal → MainAdmin DB Access

| Page Route | API Calls | MainAdmin Tables Accessed | Solution Needed |
|-----------|-----------|---------------------------|----------------|
| `/login` | `POST /auth/login` | `admin`, `buying_group_domains` | **RESOLVED** — `admin` is now in Main Admin DB; login validates directly against Main Admin DB, then session is scoped to BG DB |
| `/warehouse/receiving` | `POST /admin/warehouse/scan-box`, `GET /admin/warehouse/pending`, `GET /admin/warehouse/received` | `return_transactions` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/verification` | `GET /admin/warehouse/received` | `return_transactions` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/verification/[id]` | `GET .../verification-summary`, `POST .../start-verification`, `PATCH .../verify-v2`, `POST .../surplus`, `POST .../complete-verification` | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `warehouse_discrepancies` | **HIGH PRIORITY** - Core verification operations |
| `/warehouse/batches` | `GET/POST/DELETE /admin/batches`, `.../generate-memos` | `return_batches`, `batch_workflow_steps`, `debit_memos` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/debit-memos` | `GET/PATCH /admin/debit-memos` | `debit_memos`, `debit_memo_items` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/ra-tracking` | `GET /admin/ra-tracking`, `POST /admin/debit-memos/.../request-ra` | `debit_memos`, `ra_requests`, `shipment_groups` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/wine-cellar` | `GET/PATCH/POST /admin/wine-cellar` | `wine_cellar_items` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/destruction` | `GET/PATCH /admin/destruction` | `destruction_records` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/returns/*` | `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /return-transactions`, `GET /admin/reverse-distributors` | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `reverse_distributors`, `wine_cellar_items` | **CRITICAL** - Full return lifecycle management |
| `/policies`, `/ndc-pricing` | `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /admin/policies`, `/admin/ndc-pricing` | `manufacturer_policies`, `manufacturer_return_policies`, `ndc_pricing` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |

### Pharmacy Portal → MainAdmin DB Access

| Page Route | API Calls | MainAdmin Tables Accessed | Solution Needed |
|-----------|-----------|---------------------------|----------------|
| `/returns/*` | `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /return-transactions`, `POST /policies/check`, `POST /barcode/scan` | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `manufacturer_policies`, `ndc_pricing` | **CRITICAL** - Core pharmacy return operations |
| `/wine-cellar` | `GET /wine-cellar`, `GET /wine-cellar/stats` | `wine_cellar_items` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/returns/destruction` | `GET/PATCH /destruction` | `destruction_records` | Cross-DB query or API gateway |
| `/warehouse/verification` | `GET /admin/warehouse/received` | `return_transactions` | **AUTH ISSUE** - Pharmacy calling admin APIs |
| `/warehouse/verification/[id]` | `GET/POST/PATCH /admin/warehouse/...` (summary, start, verify-v2, surplus, complete) | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `warehouse_discrepancies` | **AUTH ISSUE** - Pharmacy calling admin APIs |
| `/warehouse/surplus` | `GET /admin/warehouse/surplus` | Surplus data from verification | **AUTH ISSUE** - Pharmacy calling admin APIs |

### Processor Portal → MainAdmin DB Access

| Operation | API Calls | MainAdmin Tables Accessed | Solution Needed |
|-----------|-----------|---------------------------|----------------|
| Return Management | `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /return-transactions`, `POST /barcode/scan`, `POST /policies/check` | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `manufacturer_policies`, `ndc_pricing` | **CRITICAL** - Processor return operations |
| Service Requests | `GET/POST /processors/service-requests` | `service_requests` (in BG DB) | No cross-DB access needed |

### RPC Functions Requiring Cross-DB Access

| RPC Function | Called From BG Context | MainAdmin Tables Used | Migration Impact |
|-------------|----------------------|---------------------|------------------|
| **Warehouse RPCs** | | | |
| `warehouse_scan_box` | Admin, Pharmacy verification | `return_transactions` | **HIGH** - Core receiving |
| `warehouse_verify_item_v2` | Admin, Pharmacy verification | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items`, `warehouse_discrepancies` | **HIGH** - Core verification |
| `warehouse_start_verification` | Admin, Pharmacy | `return_transactions` | **HIGH** |
| `warehouse_complete_verification` | Admin, Pharmacy | `return_transactions`, `return_transaction_items` | **HIGH** |
| **Return Transaction RPCs** | | | |
| `create_return_transaction` | All portals | `return_transactions` | **CRITICAL** - Return creation |
| `list_return_transactions` | All portals | `return_transactions` | **CRITICAL** - Return listing |
| `get_return_transaction_by_id` | All portals | `return_transactions` | **CRITICAL** - Return details |
| `update_return_transaction` | All portals | `return_transactions` | **CRITICAL** - Return updates |
| `add_return_transaction_item_with_validation` | All portals | `return_transaction_items` | **CRITICAL** - Item management |
| `list_return_transaction_items` | All portals | `return_transaction_items` | **CRITICAL** - Item listing |
| **Batch & Financial RPCs** | | | |
| `create_batch`, `list_batches`, `get_batch` | Admin portal | `return_batches`, `batch_workflow_steps` | **HIGH** - Batch processing |
| `generate_debit_memos_for_batch` | Admin portal | `debit_memos`, `debit_memo_items` | **HIGH** - Financial processing |
| **Wine Cellar RPCs** | | | |
| `add_to_wine_cellar`, `list_wine_cellar_items` | Admin, Pharmacy | `wine_cellar_items` | **MEDIUM** - Specialty storage |
| **Policy & Pricing RPCs** | | | |
| Policy check operations | All portals via barcode/validation | `manufacturer_policies`, `manufacturer_return_policies`, `ndc_pricing` | **HIGH** - Every return item validation |

### Critical Migration Issues

0. **Buying Group Admin Account Location (RESOLVED)**
   - `admin` table moved to Main Admin DB
   - MainAdmin creates buying group accounts; BG portal login authenticates against Main Admin DB
   - After login, session is scoped to the buying group's BG DB for all operational data
   - `get_buying_groups_list` RPC no longer requires cross-DB access for `admin` — only `admin_settings` (BG DB) may still require a cross-DB read for display purposes

1. **Pharmacy Portal Cross-Database Auth Violation**
   - Pharmacy pages call `/admin/warehouse/*` APIs directly
   - These are admin-scoped routes requiring admin permissions
   - **Solution**: Create pharmacy-specific warehouse APIs or MainAdmin BFF

2. **Return Transaction Shared Pipeline**
   - Single return pipeline shared by all portals (`authenticateAny`)
   - All portals create/update returns in MainAdmin warehouse tables
   - **Solution**: Maintain single source of truth OR implement synchronous cross-service calls

3. **High-Frequency Warehouse Operations**
   - Verification, receiving, batching are core operations
   - Multiple portals performing writes to MainAdmin warehouse tables
   - **Solution**: API gateway with proper tenant isolation

4. **Financial Chain Dependencies**
   - Returns → Batches → Debit Memos → RA → Shipments spans multiple MainAdmin tables
   - Partial migration breaks financial processing
   - **Solution**: Keep entire financial chain in MainAdmin or implement distributed transactions

5. **Policy/NDC Validation on Every Item**
   - Every barcode scan and item addition requires policy/NDC validation
   - High call volume to MainAdmin for validation
   - **Solution**: Cache policy snapshots in BG DB or high-performance MainAdmin API
## Migration Critical Considerations

### 1. Warehouse Architecture (RESOLVED)
**MainAdmin operates centralized warehouse** - all warehouse tables remain in MainAdmin DB. Buying groups create returns that are processed at the central warehouse.

### 2. Cross-Database Access Patterns
- **Buying Group → MainAdmin**: Submit returns to central warehouse
- **MainAdmin → Buying Group**: Read pharmacy/processor info for warehouse operations
- **Shared Reference Data**: Policies, NDC pricing in MainAdmin DB, accessed by buying groups

### 3. Authentication Flow
- MainAdmin auth uses `main_admin`/`sub_main_admin` tables (Main Admin DB)
- Buying group auth uses `admin` table (Main Admin DB) — accounts are created by MainAdmin and login is validated against Main Admin DB; after successful login, the session is scoped to the buying group's BG DB
- Pharmacy auth uses `pharmacy` table (BG DB)
- Tenant resolution via `buying_group_domains` (Main Admin DB)

### 4. Data Flow
1. Pharmacies create returns in BG portal
2. Returns are sent to central warehouse (MainAdmin DB)
3. MainAdmin processes returns through warehouse workflow
4. Results flow back to buying group for credits/payments

---

## Quick Reference: Portal → Primary Tables

### Main Admin Database Tables

| Portal | Primary Tables |
|--------|---------------|
| **MainAdmin** | `main_admin`, `sub_main_admin`, `buying_group_domains`, `admin`, `warehouses`, `return_batches`, `batch_workflow_steps`, `warehouse_discrepancies`, `debit_memos`, `debit_memo_items`, `ra_requests`, `shipment_groups`, `wine_cellar_items`, `destruction_records`, `reverse_distributors`, `manufacturer_policies`, `manufacturer_return_policies`, `manufacturer_policy_notes`, `non_returnable_products`, `ndc_pricing`, `distributors` |

> `return_transactions` and `return_transaction_items` are also in Main Admin DB but shared across all portals — see note below.

---

### Buying Group (BG) Database Tables

All three BG portals — **Admin, Pharmacy, and Processor** — share the same BG DB per buying group. They login via Main Admin DB (`admin` table) and then operate against their BG DB.

| Portal | Primary Tables |
|--------|---------------|
| **Admin + Pharmacy + Processor (shared BG DB)** | `admin_settings`, `pharmacy`, `pharmacy_branches`, `pharmacy_invites`, `pharmacy_inventory_items`, `pharmacy_inventory_uploads`, `pharmacy_notifications`, `pharmacy_payments`, `processors`, `processor_store_assignments`, `processor_notifications`, `service_requests`, `service_request_assignments`, `marketplace_deals`, `marketplace_orders`, `marketplace_cart_items`, `products`, `custom_packages`, `custom_package_items`, `product_list_items`, `inventory_items`, `inventory_reminders`, `subscriptions`, `subscription_plans`, `uploaded_documents`, `refresh_tokens`, `settings`, `returns`, `return_items`, `return_reports`, `email_logs`, `email_logs_with_memo_info` |

---

### Cross-DB Note: `return_transactions` & `return_transaction_items`

These two tables live in **Main Admin DB** (central warehouse) but are accessed by **all portals** (Admin, Pharmacy, Processor) as part of the return submission and lifecycle flow. They are the primary cross-DB access point for BG portals.

---

*Document reflects the centralized warehouse architecture where MainAdmin operates warehouse operations for all buying groups.*
